<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about win10)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/cat_win10.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 31 Mar 2017 06:33:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>Win10修改MAC地址</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/win10xiu-gai-macdi-zhi/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;1、打开注册表编辑器，“运行”-&amp;gt;“regedit”。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、找到如下路径，得到下图：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Class\{4D36E972-E325-11CE-BFC1-08002bE10318}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/modifymac1.PNG" src="https://github.com/longlongpicture/myblogpicture/raw/master/modifymac1.PNG"&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、右击"0003"-&amp;gt;"新建"-&amp;gt;"字符串值"-&amp;gt;"NetworkAddress"。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4、双击“NetworkAddress”，输入新的MAC地址值，比如“0028F80AF812”。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5、点击“确定”，重启电脑即可。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Network</category><category>win10</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/win10xiu-gai-macdi-zhi/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 31 Mar 2017 04:15:05 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>win10双屏下隐藏非主屏任务栏</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/win10shuang-ping-xia-yin-cang-fei-zhu-ping-ren-wu-lan/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;win10双屏下默认都有任务栏，貌似占用了有限的可视空间，可以通过如下方法关闭非主屏的任务栏。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;通过“设置”-&amp;gt;“系统”-&amp;gt;“显示”，设置主屏；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;右击任务栏，点击“属性”；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;去掉“在所有显示器上显示任务栏”前面的勾，点击“确定”即可。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>win10</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/win10shuang-ping-xia-yin-cang-fei-zhu-ping-ren-wu-lan/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 12 Jan 2017 10:46:17 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>